features.name: FtsK_SpoIIIE ATP binding P-loop motif. it is found in the FtsK cell division protein from E. coli and the stage III sporulation protein E SpoIIIE, which has roles in regulation of prespore specific gene expression in B. subtilis. a mutation in FtsK causes a temperature sensitive block in cell division and it is involved in peptidoglycan synthesis or modification. the SpoIIIE protein is implicated in intercellular chromosomal DNA transfer
